{
	"folder": "GAaTOyY6q3hBxDlY",
	"name": "Fire Elemental Form",
	"type": "feat",
	"_id": "Nh8sq9EtMjMjux4F",
	"img": "icons/magic/fire/elemental-fire-humanoid.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p>You transform into an hybrid &amp;reference[humanoid] and fire &amp;reference[elemental] form, your body made of (mostly) harmless flames that dance in the air.</p><p><span><strong>Bonus Action</strong> </span>- Self - 10 Minutes -@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Ik6ei7V7ryr5XVoe]{3 Sorcery Points} - Magical</p><p>You choose whether your equipment falls to the ground in your space, merges into your new form, or if you continue to visibly wear it.</p><ul><li><p>You are immune to &amp;reference[fire] damage and resistant to &amp;reference[radiant] damage.</p></li><li><p>You are immune to &amp;reference[poison] damage and the &amp;reference[poisoned apply=false] condition.</p></li><li><p>You are immune to the &amp;reference[grappled], &amp;reference[petrified], and &amp;reference[restrained apply=false] conditions.</p></li><li><p>You shed bright light in a 30 ft. radius and dim light in a 60 ft. radius.</p></li><li><p>You can squeeze through gaps as small as 1 inch wide.</p></li><li><p>You no longer have normal bodily functions. You don't breathe, can't bleed, be magically aged, or otherwise do anything that relies on your normal biological functions.</p></li></ul><p>You can revert to your normal form using a bonus action. You also revert to your normal form if you are reduced to 0 hit points.</p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
